<p>The Lumby Branch is located in the Lumby Community Centre.</p>
<p>When the library is closed there is a book drop bin located on the side of the walkway entering the building.</p>
<p>Please find our events below on the branch calendar, or search the <a href="news-events/event-search">ORL Calendar of Events</a>.</p></div>
